  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 4230393856
    m_Localized: "Was the filling kidnapped? Because I can\u2019t find it here"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 36560089088
    m_Localized: If the goal was to sell me gourmet air, congratulations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83129446400
    m_Localized: "It\u2019s so greasy you could fry another pastel with this one."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 89508982784
    m_Localized: "I don\u2019t remember ordering a disappointment-flavored pastel."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 106894372864
    m_Localized: "If this is the \u2018house flavor,\u2019 the house clearly needs
      a renovation"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
